Name: Yang2020 Path To Presidency
About the game: The Andrew Yang video game is finally here! Does the 'longer than longshot' candidate have what it takes to beat the competition and take back the White House ? STORY MODE With a compelling story mode you play as Andrew Yang on the path to presidency! Within the Story mode you will be able to unlock stages and characters to use in VERSUS MODE VERSUS MODE Play one on one against your friends in local multiplayer matches or against the cpu. Unlock characters including Bernie Sanders , Elizabeth Warren even Donald Trump ! and many more! GAMEPLAY This game is a classic one on one fighting game, full of colourful characters and quirky special moves.
